for metric in config['metrics']:
    if metric['type'] == 'cpu' and psutil.cpu_percent() > metric['threshold']:
        print(f"ALERT: CPU usage above {metric['threshold']}%")

Explanation:
Use YAML to define monitoring thresholds dynamically.

